text: GDH may refer to: * Gajirrabeng dialect, native to Australia * GDH 559, a Thai film production company * Glutamate dehydrogenase * Gonzo (company), previously GDH K.K., a Japanese anime studio * Gordon Hill railway station, in London * Gosford Hospital * Grand Ducal Highness * Guangdong Holdings, a Chinese holding company
